<li>Controller: avoid startup errors when bitbucket credentials are empty</=
li>
<li>Builder: fix permissions for non-root user (used for specific Maven bui=
lds)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Features</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>UI: add info link explaining how to create a Bitbucket access tokens</l=
i>
</ul>
<p>See the full Changelog <a href=3D"https://code.sbb.ch/projects/KD_ESTA/r=
